WEBVTT

00:06:28.580 --> 00:06:30.535
and compassion for others.

00:06:32.572 --> 00:06:35.574
We live in a world filled with hate:

00:06:35.598 --> 00:06:37.196
building walls,

00:06:37.220 --> 00:06:38.514
Brexit,

00:06:38.538 --> 00:06:42.017
xenophobia here on the African continent.

00:06:43.326 --> 00:06:45.726
Multiculturalism can be an answer

00:06:45.750 --> 00:06:49.376
to many of these worst human qualities.

00:06:51.308 --> 00:06:54.096
Today, I challenge you

00:06:54.120 --> 00:06:58.034
to help a young child
experience multiculturalism.

00:06:59.165 --> 00:07:03.248
I guarantee you
that will enrich their life,